rows.label: qst105908_msg001
rows.name:
Mo-mo? Do you want Kisasa
to rank you too, mo?

rows.label: qst105908_msg002
rows.name: Alright, mo. Then pay 1,000G, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg003
rows.name: The fee for ranking is 1,000G, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg005
rows.name:
U-Ugh... Alright, mo. I'll settle
for 500G, mo. So please don't
look at me like that, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg006
rows.name: Well then, let's get back to it, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg007
rows.name:
A salvager's rank is determined
by the total value of everything
you've salvaged so far, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg008
rows.name:
We'll start at the beginner rank, mo.
Once you've salvaged a lot of amazing
things, come back to get ranked, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg009
rows.name:
But since there's a 500G fee each
time, it might be better to come after
you've found a decent amount, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg010
rows.name:
Also, you can only go up one rank at
a time, so please understand, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg101
rows.name: Get a ranking check from Limlim, mo?

rows.label: qst105908_msg102
rows.name: Get a ranking check?

rows.label: qst105908_msg103
rows.name: Get checked

rows.label: qst105908_msg104
rows.name: Don't get checked

rows.label: qst105908_msg105
rows.name:
Roger, mo! Now, let's
get to ranking, mo!

rows.label: qst105908_msg106
rows.name: Your salvager rank is...

rows.label: qst105908_msg107
rows.name: Beginner, mo. Still a fledgling, mo!

rows.label: qst105908_msg108
rows.name:
Intermediate, mo. Promoted from
fledgling to apprentice, mo!

rows.label: qst105908_msg109
rows.name:
Advanced, mo! You've finally
come this far, mo. The top is
just around the corner, mo!

rows.label: qst105908_msg110
rows.name:
Congratulations, Master, mo!
Keep up the good work, mo!

rows.label: qst105908_msg111
rows.name:
Roger, mo. When you want
to get ranked, just come
to Limlim anytime, mo.

rows.label: qst105908_msg201
rows.name:
You have become a Master.
Keep up the good work.
